# Vault Factory Contract

Deploy Vaults like a master!.

Each new Factory has a different bytecode (library address is forced manually input)

Name in parity registry: vaultfactory-v2

Factory Library at:
```
Mainnet:
Ropsten: d129bbccd69ff01e0614e50ec6b202d0d85c0ae1
Kovan: e03284980c0152ec7cedd3ae94b31c0aa535aff9
```

Kovan:
